element.name: The Birds by Windsockers, Multi-cache (1/1.5)

long-description.p:
Take a quick tour of some of the many Sculptures in the seaside town of Skerries.
for the lazy cachers this can be all done as a drive by cache.

At the above location take note of the following:
How many letters are in the name call this A
How many words make up the artists name call the answer B
What is the first digit of the year call this C
What is the last digit of the year call this D

Go to N53 35.1B(A-B) W6 06.CD1
At this location take note of the following:
How many birds are there call this E
What is the first digit of the year call this F
What is the third digit of the year call this G
What is the last digit of the year call this H

Go to N53 34.(F+H)G(H*D) W6 06.BD(E*C)
At this location take note of the following:
How many birds are there call this I
What is the last digit of the year call this J
How many single rocks are there call this K

The cache can be found at:
N53 34.(A-E)(J-C)(H+F) W6 06.(I-C)KJ
Please retrieve and replace the cache with extreme care to Prevent Muggles from Discovering the cache.

ul.li:
2010-04-20T19:00:00Z : Found it by dsquaredd2
Biggest caching day for D2D2 today with a cache run with the owner, Windsockers! We went on a circuit beginning with Newgrange and ending in the Skerries finding and maintaining caches. A fun day, each location was unique. This was the twentieth. TFTC!

2010-04-18T19:00:00Z : Found it by rooske
A lovely walk around Skerries, lots of muggles around managed to retriev cach while tying my laces

2010-03-16T19:00:00Z : Found it by Peta Amalka
Very enjoyable caching :-) We had very cold and windy day in Skerries but the walk was lovely and I will be definelly back to enjoy this spectacular town and scenery again. TFTC

2010-03-16T19:00:00Z : Found it by lenik1
Found it after a nice stroll round Skerries with my friends. We enjoyed the walk, it was very cold and windy though. In spite of that we had a nice time in Skerries today! TFTC

2010-01-17T20:00:00Z : Found it by DoJoPa
Lovely walk on a sunny winter day with a lot of new impressions of Skerries. TFTC!
